{"id":"a75cd34c-b952-4eac-a738-314db1503596","name":"Gold City (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 135, 252);\"><strong><em>Beauty Of The Century<br>シチー</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">───── ⋆ ✦ ⋆ ─────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/h4uhJYlEKwrQ2yxa_SVqu.webp\" style=\"width: 641px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">───── ⋆ ✦ ⋆ ─────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>A blunt racer and the gold standard in racing and beauty.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>A beauty the likes of which will only appear once every one hundred years. She's been a model for as long as she can remember, and has always acted the part. She realized one day, however, that running is her true heart's desire. Since then, she has raced ever forward so that she may be recognized not for her looks, but for her talent. She's understood most by her good friend Tosen Jordan.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 135, 252);\"><br><strong><em>\"Right now, I'm just a pretty face... but not for long!\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xckGdbPZ42WmxE2MlQTYq.webp\" style=\"width: 564px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">───── ⋆ ✦ ⋆ ─────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 135, 252);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 135, 252);\"><strong><br></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 39, 46);\"><strong><em>1) You wake her up for early morning drills.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 135, 252);\"><strong><em>2) A magazine shoot</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 39, 46);\"><strong><em>3) Time at the beach</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 135, 252);\"><strong><em>4) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ErvKF9V2I5mfcaGy8BHam.webp\" style=\"width: 597px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">───── ⋆ ✦ ⋆ ─────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Pondering.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Also here's the 2 girls who won the random pick.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br>JP</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/dmsSkdOv4VLD5_X7PAkQP.webp\" style=\"width: 525px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br>Global</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/F0TGHJ_uBq7PyfluWJ0f4.webp\" style=\"width: 515px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">───── ⋆ ✦ ⋆ ─────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/132924018\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/pine_pinepin/status/1874100545637802199/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@pine_pinepin</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/132123840\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/133688783\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"3_lEUXBd7sWZi8p2U31C-.webp","crea